    dc:title "Revision of ‘ Horatia’ snails (Mollusca: Gastropoda: Hydrobiidae sensu lato) from South Caucasus with description of two new genera" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5194253>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5194257>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5194251> ;
